@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix soma: <http://www.ease-crc.org/ont/SOMA.owl#> .
@prefix dul: <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#> .
@prefix geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix psr: <https://w3id.org/psr-action#> .

### Knowledge Graph of Actions

## Instruction
psr:restore_kitchen a psr:Instruction ;
  psr:hasNaturalLanguage "Restore the kitchen to an organized state by identifying all misplaced items and returning them to their standard storage locations based on their type and function."@en .

## Workflow
psr:workflow_1 a psr:Workflow .

## Actions
psr:pick_up_item_1 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PickingUp .

psr:pick_up_item_2 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PickingUp .

psr:pick_up_item_3 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PickingUp .

psr:pick_up_item_4 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PickingUp .

psr:pick_up_item_5 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PickingUp .

psr:place_item_1 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PuttingDown .

psr:place_item_2 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PuttingDown .

psr:place_item_3 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PuttingDown .

psr:place_item_4 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PuttingDown .

psr:place_item_5 a dul:Action ;
  psr:isAffordedBy soma:PuttingDown .

## Relationships
psr:restore_kitchen psr:hasWorkflow psr:workflow_1 .

psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:pick_up_item_1 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:pick_up_item_2 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:pick_up_item_3 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:pick_up_item_4 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:pick_up_item_5 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:place_item_1 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:place_item_2 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:place_item_3 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:place_item_4 .
psr:workflow_1 psr:hasAction psr:place_item_5 .

psr:pick_up_item_1 psr:precedes psr:place_item_1 .
psr:pick_up_item_2 psr:precedes psr:place_item_2 .
psr:pick_up_item_3 psr:precedes psr:place_item_3 .
psr:pick_up_item_4 psr:precedes psr:place_item_4 .
psr:pick_up_item_5 psr:precedes psr:place_item_5 .

## Objects and Affordances
psr:table a psr:Component, psr:Appliance .

psr:refrigerator a psr:Component, psr:Appliance .

psr:cabinet a psr:Component, psr:Furniture .

psr:cup a psr:Object .

psr:plate a psr:Object .

psr:book a psr:Object .

psr:bottle a psr:Object .

psr:box a psr:Object .

psr:jar a psr:Object .

## Execution
psr:pick_up_item_1 psr:actsOn psr:cup .
psr:pick_up_item_2 psr:actsOn psr:bottle .
psr:pick_up_item_3 psr:actsOn psr:box .
psr:pick_up_item_4 psr:actsOn psr:plate .
psr:pick_up_item_5 psr:actsOn psr:jar .

psr:place_item_1 psr:actsOn psr:cabinet .
psr:place_item_2 psr:actsOn psr:refrigerator .
psr:place_item_3 psr:actsOn psr:cabinet .
psr:place_item_4 psr:actsOn psr:cabinet .
psr:place_item_5 psr:actsOn psr:cabinet .
